name: Bunny Eats
description:
Deliver with Bunny Eats

No boss. Flexible schedule. Quick pay.

Now you can make money carrots by delivering food orders that people rabbits crave using the Bunny Eats app — all while exploring your island.

                                              

This game was made for the sim-jam.

The wonderful music in this game is part of the CC-BY albums by:

James Hammond - https://jameshammondrf.bandcamp.com/

Bloma - https://bloma.bandcamp.com

This game was developed mostly live at the Godot Engine discord server. So I would like to thank everyone there for their valuable comments and suggestions.
